<document>
  <properties>
    <title>Document panel</title>
  </properties>

  <body>
   <section name="Document panel">
      <span class="shortdesc">What and where is the document panel?</span>

    <div class='group'>
     <div class='screenshot'>
      <img src="../../../../images/screenshots/cms_M9/contribs/document_panel.png" 
       alt='document panel'/>
     </div>
     <p>
      The document panel. 
      <span class='rewrite'>Is for content. Call it content panel?</span>
     </p>   
    </div>

    <p>
     In the <i>document panel</i> a document can be <a href='./edit_mode.html'>changed</a> or
     <a href='./review_mode.html'>reviewed</a>
     The <i>document panel</i> may hold several 
     <a href='document_card.html'>document cards</a>, of which one is visible.
     Tabs of all cards are visible at the upper edge of the <i>document panel</i>. 
     Several documents card can be open on the documents panel at any time. 
     You can click on a tab to put another document card on top, so that you
     can see it. 
    </p>

   </section>
  </body>
